name: TikkiBunga's Island
description:
Fullscreen for best experience!

Expand your village by feeding the one true giant frog god, Tikki Bunga.

Your villagers are lazy and slow, keep them happy and productive by building gardens. Feed happy villagers to Tikki Bunga in exchange for souls. Exchange souls for a new generation of villagers.

Expand and prosper.

Controls:

WASD - Camera Movement

X - Z - Camera Zoom

Left click - Interact

Esc - Pause, Audio settings

Entry for Brackey's Jam 2023.1

Made in under a weeek by one person, using Unity, Aseprite, Audacity, Gimp and Stable Diffusion.
Music by ummbrella

Theme: An end is a new beginning.
